==German==
===Noun===
'''Blech''' ''n'' (''pl'' Bleche)
# [[sheet]] (out of metal)
# [[Brass]] (informal, musical, ''singulare tantum'') collective term for all brass instruments, or all brass players, etc.
: ''„Das Blech spielt bitte mal alleine!“ rief der Dirigent.''
: The conductor demanded loudly: „Brass play on their own now, please!“

